Cook apples in a large saucepan with water, simmering over medium-low heat until apples are tender, about 15 to 20 minutes. Process cooked apples through a food mill or puree in a blender or food processor. Stir in the SPLENDA(R) No Calorie Sweetener with Fiber, lemon juice, and cinnamon. Return to sauce pan and cook over medium heat for about 3 to 5 minutes.